    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Both employers and students have a lot to gain from the Employer Mentoring Programme. </p>
<p>The employer/mentee relationship allows students to develop their employability skills while gaining a close insight into a particular job or sector. At the same time employers experience the rewards of being a mentor and of sharing their knowledge with enthusiastic students.</p>]]></Value>
